[06/10/2018 05:34:20] <font color="#ffffff">su diafanidad,</font>
[06/10/2018 05:34:22] <font color="#ffffff">admirar la complejidad</font>
[06/10/2018 05:34:22] <font color="#ffffff">de su estructura,</font>
